item.description:
Report X-2023120518

Identified by scraper @ 2023-12-30T17:46:52+00:00

  • Incident Date: 2023-12-06
  • City: LOUISVILLE
  • State: KY
  • Report Type: Undeclared Shipment with no Release
  • Mode Of Transportation: Air
  • Carrier/Reporter: UNITED PARCEL SERVICE CO.
  • Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Hazmat Injuries: 0
  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Description: PACKAGE WAS WET FROM RAIN. DURING PACKAGE REWRAP FLAMMABLE LIQUID CONTENTS WERE DISCOVERED. THERE ARE TWO CONTAINERS OF ICLEAN DOG WASH DISINFECTANT X 5 LITERS. THERMAL TRACKING LABEL AND INVOICE DESCRIPTION IS DOG WASH PARTS. THERE ARE NO DANGEROUS GOODS MARKS OR LABELS ON THE OUTER BOX TO INDICATE FLAMMABLE LIQUID CONTENTS WERE BEING SHIPPED FROM THE NETHERLANDS TO THE USA. THE PACKAGE WAS SHIPPED USING UPS ACCOUNT 841E88, ICLEAN CARWASH TECHNOLOGIES, AMBACHTSTRAAT 46, VENRAY NETHERLANDS 5804CD.
